   Giovanni Bistoni       : ED, misc. LED, open-shell LED, HFLD
   Martin Brehm           : Molecular dynamics
   Dmytro Bykov           : SCF Hessian
   Vijay G. Chilkuri      : MRCI spin determinant printing, contributions to CSF-ICE
